{subhead}Gary Peake suffered heart attack, is on the way of recovery (16/12/02){def}
{left}
{pp}
Gary suffered a heart attack over the weekend but is now back at home
and on the way to a full recovery. He is following doctors orders to
get plenty of rest and stay away from email.
{pp}
He has asked me to thank you for keeping him in your thoughts and for
your best wishes. He hopes to be back on email towards the end of the week.
{pp}